song_lyrics: Vishwakā kalyāṇ ho, karma mangal ho hamāre;
Nāth sarjan yā visarjan, bāt basme hai tere;
Denā charnome jagā, ham sharaṇme āye tere... 1
He Prabhu aisī do shakti, ham sadāchārī bane;
Satya nīti dharma bhakti, sevā vrat dhārī bane... 2
Pragaṭ Prabhujī āp nishdin, ānkhome baske rahe;
Jāge to darshan tumhāre, soye to sapne tere... 3
title: Mangalam shubh mangalam He Prabhu he mangaldātā
